Text:
@PeterDutton_MP People are rightly concerned about their privacy. 

You are talking about banning under 16s from social media for their mental health, yet still allowing them to access hard core porn. 

The only way it makes sense is if you want to digitally ID everyone and police their posts.

@AleximusPrime I thought the sabbath is actually saturday? XD

work mostly. but in general I want weekends to be for me and my rest for physical/mental health.
it might include less social media, but that also depends on how I feel lol.

@natr66 @welchy3319 FYI, my wall is NOT for debates, ONLY share opinions and perspectives.  Am not on here to win points otherwise social media becomes so toxic

My SM policy is 24 hours and that's it.  It's a new day.  Never drag on longer than that.  It's not good for our mental health.

All best.
